        @BeanProperty(value="query")
public String getQuery()
        The equivalent of one Gnip PowerTrack rule, with up to 2048 characters (and no limits on the number of positive and negative clauses). This parameter should include ALL portions of the PowerTrack rule, including all operators, and portions of the rule should not be separated into other parameters of the query. (Required)

public String getFromDate()
        The oldest UTC timestamp (back to 3/21/2006) from which the activities will be provided. Timestamp is in minute granularity and is inclusive (i.e. 12:00 includes the 00 minute).
